title: Boeing assembly workers go on strike - Main Stream Videos
text: Boeing assembly workers went on strike early Friday morning after 95% of the union members rejected the company’s latest tentative contract, essentially shutting down production at factories in the Seattle area. CBS News senior transportation correspondent Kris Van Cleave has more.
